'''Abramidze''' ({{lang-ka|<U+10D0><U+10D1><U+10E0><U+10D0><U+10DB><U+10D8><U+10EB><U+10D4>}}) is a [[Georgian surname]]. Notable people with the surname include:

* [[Pavle Abramidze]], Soviet major-general
* [[Valeri Abramidze]], Georgian footballer

